headline: Elon Musk Buying MSNBC? A Difficult Feat, Because It Isn’t for Sale
summary: Can  Elon Musk  make a run at acquiring MSNBC?  Last week,  Comcast  said it was moving forward with a plan to spin off its NBCUniversal cable networks into a separate company.  It is unclear how serious Musk is about MSNBC, but buying the network wouldn’t be an easy feat.
